704095f-a.title: Brooklyn: Emmons Avenue - 15th Street
704095f-a.text:
Emmons Ave., south side, east from East 15th Street. The view in
the foreground has changed. All shacks were confiscated by the City of
New York.
August 1, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
